OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly sunny
OL,6,Fstart to the evening for Orkney but
OL,7,Fcloudier over Shetland. Cloud will
OL,8,Falso spread southeast across Orkney
OL,9,Fovernight. Winds will be light and
OL,10,Fvariable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with the odd
OL,13,Fspot of drizzle in places. Cloud
OL,14,Fbreaking up during the afternoon with
OL,15,Fsunny spells developing. Light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,18,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,19,Fsettled weather through this period.
OL,20,FRather cool and cloudy at times but
OL,21,Fsome bright spells too.
